quran[47]{c,v,t}:
  72,1,"(Nkͻmhyεni), ka sε: “Yayi akyerε me sε, Jinn fekuo bi tiee (Qur’aan yi mu nsεm na wͻ’kͻeε no), wͻ’ka kyerεε (wͻn nkorͻfoͻ) sε: ”Nokorε sε, y’ate akenkan bi a εyε nwanwa"
  72,2,"Ɛkyerε kwan kͻ kwan tenenee no so, enti yε’deε y’agye adi, na yεnnfa obiara mmata ye’Wura Nyankopͻn ho (nnsom no)"
  72,3,"Nokorε sε, Ɔne ye’Wura (Nyankopͻn), Animuonyam Hene a Netumi korͻn no, Onni yere na Onni ba nso"
  72,4,Nokorɛ sɛ nkwaseafoͻ bi a εwͻ yεn mu no twa nkontompo a εborosoᴐ paa deto Nyankopͻn so
  72,5,"Yε’deε na yε’dwen sε, onipa ne Jinn ntumi ntwa nkontompo nnto Nyankopͻn so"
  72,6,"Nokorε sε, mmarima no bi wͻ nnipa mu a, wͻ’hwehwε ntwitwageε firi Jinn mmarima no mu bi hͻ, enti wͻ’ma (nnipa no) tͻkͻso di nsεmmͻne"
  72,7,"Nokorε sε, wᴐ’dwen sεdeε mo (nnipa no mu bi) dwen sε Nyankopͻn nnsoma (ᴐsomafoͻ) biara no"
  72,8,"Nokorε sε, na yεrehwehwε (kwan) sε, yεbeduru ͻsoro hͻ (akͻtie adwen a, εhͻfoͻ no refa), nanso yehunuu sε, awεnfoͻ ahoͻdenfoͻ ne ogya tanaa ayε hͻ mma"
  72,9,"Na anka yεkͻtena (ͻsoro) tenabea no mu baabi sεdeε yεbεtie (ͻsoro asafo no adwen a, wͻ’refa). Na seesei deε obi a (ͻbεkͻ hͻ) akotie no, ͻbεkͻ akͻto ogya tanaa a εretwεn no"
  72,10,"Nokorε nso sε yɛ’nnnim sε bͻne na Ɔrehwehwε ama asaase so foͻ, anaasε ͻkwan kyerε bi na wͻn Wura Nyankopͻn rehwehwε ama wͻn"
  72,11,"Nokorε sε yεn mu bi yε apapafoͻ, na ebinom nso nte saa, yegu ahodoͻ a yε’nam akwan sononko-sononko"
  72,12,"Yenim yie sε, yenntumi nwane Nyankopͻn wͻ asaase yi so, na yenntumi nso nntu nwane no (wͻ ewiem)"
  72,13,"Enti εberε a yε’tee tenenee no ho asεm no, yε’gye dii. Na obi a ͻbεgye Nyankopͻn adie no, onsuro papa ho asisie (sε ne papa so bεteε), anaa bͻne nso ho asisie (sε yεde bͻne a ͻnyͻeε bεma no)"
  72,14,"Yεn mu bi yε Muslimifoͻ, εna yεn mu bi nso ayera anaa wͻn amane afri kwan tenenee no soͻ. Enti obi a ͻbεyε Muslim aberε ne ho ase (ama Nyankopͻn) no, saa nkorͻfoͻ no na wᴐn afa tenenee kwan no"
  72,15,Na mmom ayerafoͻ no deε wͻ’ne Amane-hunu gya no nnyentia no
  72,16,"Sε wͻ’regyina pintinn wͻ ͻkwan tenenee no so a, anka Yε’bεma wͻn nsuo anom ama abu (wͻn) so"
  72,17,"Sεdeε Yε’de bεyε wͻn nsͻhwε. Na obi a ͻbεtwe ne ho afri ne Wura Nyankopͻn Afutusεm no ho no, Ɔbεma no akͻ asotwee kεseε paa mu"
  72,18,"Nokorε sε, Nyamefrε bea biara wͻ Nyankopͻn, enti monhwε na moannsu anfrε obiara (wͻ hͻ) ka Nyankopͻn nko ara ho"
  72,19,"Nokorε sε, εberε a Nyankopͻn akoa (Muhammad) gyina hͻ rebͻ mpae sufrε no no, εkaa kakraabi sε anka (Jinnfoͻ no) kͻkyere guu no so wͻ akͻnkͻn so"
  72,20,"(Nkͻmhyεni), ka sε: “Medeε me Wura Nyankopͻn na mesu frε no, na mennfa biribi mmata ne ho “"
  72,21,"Ka sε: “Medeε menni bͻne anaasε papa so tumi bi dema mo’’"
  72,22,"Ka sε: “Obiara nntumi nnye me mfiri Nyankopͻn nsam, na mefri n’akyi nso a mennya dwanekͻ bea"
  72,23,"Mmom (m’adwuma nesε) mεbͻ nsεm a efiri Nyankopͻn hͻ no ho dawuro. Enti obi a ͻbεte Nyankopͻn ne Ne Somafoͻ no so atua no, nokorε sε, ͻwͻ Amanhunu gya a, ͻbεtena mu afe bͻͻ"
  72,24,"(Abosomsomfoͻ no de asoͻden saa ara) kͻpem εberε a, wͻ’behunu deε yahyε wͻn ho bͻ no, εhͻ na wͻ’behunu obi a n’aboafoͻ nni ahoͻden na (wͻn) dodoͻ nso yε kakraabi"
  72,25,"(Nkͻmhyεni), ka sε: “Medeε mennim sε deε yahyε mo ho bͻ no abεn, anaasε me Wura Nyankopͻn de bεhyε εberε tenten bi"
  72,26,"Ahuntasεm mu Nimdefoͻ (Nyame), Ɔnna N’ahuntasεm adi nnkyerε obiara"
  72,27,"Gyesε Ɔsomani a W’ayi no. Nokorε sε, Ɔma Awεnfoͻ di n’anim ne n’akyi"
  72,28,"Sεdeε Obεhunu sε ampa, wͻ’abͻ wͻn Wura Nyankopͻn asεm no ho dawuro. (Ne nimdeε) atwa deε εwͻ wͻn hͻ no (nyinaa) ho ahyia, na Wakan biribiara nso dodoͻ, (anaasε Onim biribiara dodoͻ)"
  73,1,Wo a wode bomo anaa ntoma akata wo ho
  73,2,"Sͻre anadwo (bͻ mpaeε), na fa (εberε) kakraabi (da gye wa’home)"
  73,3,"Fa anadwo no mu fa (bͻ mpaeε), anaasε te (εberε) no so kakra"
  73,4,Anaasε fa (εberε no) bi ka ho; na fa ntooboaseε kenkan Qur’aan no sεdeε efata ma ԑho nte
  73,5,"Nokorε sε, Yε’de asεm a, emu yε duro paa bεma wo"
  73,6,"Nokorε sε, anadwo berε mpaebͻ (Tahajud) no emu yε du, etu awͻse, na εma asεm no nso kͻ (onipa no mu) anaasε εma no te asεm no ase yie"
  73,7,"Nokorj sj adekyej (berj) mu no,wo wc dwumadie pii"
  73,8,"Na bͻ wo Wura Nyankopͻn abodin, na fa woho ma no kora-kora-kora"
  73,9,"Apueε ne Atͻeε Wura ne no, Awurade foforͻ biara nnihͻ ka ne ho, enti fa no yε wo Kyitaafoͻ"
  73,10,"Na si aboterε wͻ deε wͻ’rekeka no ho, na fa kwan pa so twe wo ho fri wͻn ho"
  73,11,"Na gyae Mene wͻn a, wͻ’fa no atorᴐsԑm no, wͻn a wͻ’anya wͻn ho no; na wodeε to wobo ase ma wͻn kakra"
  73,12,"Nokorε sε, Yεn hͻ na dadewεnfoͻ ne Amanehunu gya wͻ"
  73,13,"Ɛne aduane a, ehia anaa etwi (onipa mene mu) ne asotwee a εyε ya paa (no nso wͻ)"
  73,14,"Ɛda no a asaase ne mmepͻ bεwoso nwoso kεseε no, mmepͻ no bεyε sε anwea a yaboa ano na εredwirie"
  73,15,"Nokorε sε, Y’asoma Ɔsomafoͻ aba monkyεn a ͻrebedi moho adanseε, sεdeε Yε’somaa Ɔsomafoͻ (Mose) kͻͻ Farao hͻ no"
  73,16,"Nanso Farao yεε asoͻden tiaa Ɔsomafoͻ (Mose), enti Yε’sͻͻ no mu nsͻdene"
  73,17,"Sε moannye Ɛda a εbεma nkͻdaa afu dwono no anni a, sεn na mobesi abͻ moho ban (wͻ saa Da no a)"
  73,18,Ɔsoro besunsuan asin-asin wͻ mu no? Nyankopͻn bͻhyε deε εyε hͻ
  73,19,"Nokorε sε, woi yε Afutusεm, enti obi a ͻpε no ͻnfa kwan a εkͻ ne Wura Nyankopͻn hͻ no so"